data.description: Active Under Contract - Accepting Back Up Offers. **Newer Roof 2022**Welcome to an extraordinary 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that masterfully balances modern living with comfort. Spanning 2116 livable square feet, this residence offers abundant space for relaxation and privacy, while wide sliding glass doors fill the living areas with natural light, seamlessly connecting the indoors with the inviting back lanai.Step outside to experience the oasis-like allure. The refreshing pool beckons for hours of leisure, enhanced by the scenic views from the back lanai - a perfect space for relaxation, entertaining, and tranquil enjoyment.Beyond its inherent charm, this home boasts an array of recent upgrades that elevate its appeal. A new roof was completed in 2022, ensuring both durability and peace of mind. Inside, the master bathroom exudes elegance with new Quartz countertops, cabinets, and light fixtures. The guest bathroom also stands renewed with a new marble countertop and cabinets. The pool features a new Salt water system, self-cleaning mechanism, pump, and lights, offering modern convenience.The property's exterior is equally enhanced with a new 6-foot privacy vinyl fence, adding charm and seclusion. New landscaping, including palm trees and sprinklers, grace both front and back yards. Inside, new ceiling fans ensure comfort, while an in-wall vacuum system streamlines maintenance.The kitchen, a hub of activity, now boasts new countertops, while even the outside shower by the pool is thoughtfully new. This residence isn't just a house; it's an embodiment of thoughtful design, comfort, and innovation. The seamless integration of indoor and outdoor living spaces, coupled with an array of modern features, makes this property an irresistible opportunity.
